					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Yesterday was my birthday and by extension Donkman's, thought we'd write him a proper birthday tale. We hope you enjoy!</p> <p>Big thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1582589073" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span> for their excellent work on this. As always, it was a pleasure working with them.</p> <p>Critters: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5028224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1582589073" alt="Crashington" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5028224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" >Crashington</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/popsioak" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5231418&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1582589073" alt="Popsioak" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5231418)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/popsioak" >Popsioak</a></span></p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">images</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">images</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Donk Mom:<br /> <a href="https://commons.m.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Mr._Davies_and_donkey,_Tal-y-bont_(Caerhun,_Caern)_NLW3362988.JPG">https://commons.m.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Mr._Davies_and_donkey,_Tal-y-bont